  {
    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "I am not sure that Panel widget will change the label provided in `connectCurrentRefinements` ?\r\nObjective is to create beautiful pills which allow to clear some filters.\r\n\r\nProblem is that `connectCurrentRefinements` give us the current refinements with their associated label.\r\nThese labels are customizable for some connectors (ex : connectToggleRefinement) but not for others (ex : connectRefinementList).\r\n\r\nCurrent workaround we did is to do some Regexp Replace of labels given in `connectCurrentRefinements` to do beautiful display.\r\nFor example : \r\n`new RegExp('(.+) <= stock.remainingQuantity'` => `'Stock min.: $1'`",
